Hi,

> Anyone have code for handling two mice inputs, ie joystick port used
> for a second mouse?

There are lots of ways to impliment it but the basic method
is based aroun the values peeked at at:-

Peek.b($dff00d) ; X speed...
Peek.b($dff00c) ; Y speed...

I'm sure you can take it from there...

Cheers,

