> PowerUP=3D 1 or *more* PowerPC CPU's
> WarpUP=3D 1 and *1 only* PowerPC CPU's.

Wrong. PowerUP=3D 1 PPC, AND one CISC CPU.
WarpUP (WarpOS) =3D Anynumber of combinations, preferably no CISC.

