ve
another soul before it is too late.

> The fact is there are MANY MANY very happy AFS and PFS2 users.

Yeah, who are QUITE outnumbered by happy FFS users.

> Its also a fact that FFS is not very stable at all.

Ehm, say that again ? Well, maybe not the early versions, but the early
versions of PFS where downright dangerous. I have yet to experience (in 7=

