works with any accelerator system compliant (not the MTec ones and so). I=
t is
sold with a Gfx card, the Pixel64 one. As it is full ISA compliant, you c=
an
buy a cheap serial and/or parallel pc card and plug into it to get runnin=
g :-)

Currently, they have the Pixel64 and ser/par cards working. Soon they wil=
l
have a Ethernet driver and later a MusicCard driver...

I can sold you new ones for 50000 pts (=CE230?). If you want one, just se=
nt me
the money by "postal money order". It will be shipped to your house direc=
tly
