------------------------------------------------------

Voteing Results For November 98 

Yes - 2
No  - 0

Its not a lot so ill keep the voteing open until the
end of Jan 1999

------------------------------------------------------

Time To VOTE ............

Should I Continue The Blits List Guide ??

YES - Then E-Mail blg.yes@0nline.freeserve.co.uk

NO - Then E-Mail blg.no@0nline.freeserve.co.uk

Voteing Closes At the END OF Jan 1999.

If i get no/few VOTES then i will Stop produceing the Guide
and Jan 1999 will be the LAST ONE.
-------------------------------------------------------

