l the 
messages anyway, it would be a good record of whats been happening (dare I=
 even 
say a reference manual, in case no-one keeps the one Holy-grail message). =
And 
what happens to all the Blitzers not on the list (or internet at all). I t=
hink 
AF put this on their CD every month, but many people may still not be awar=
e of 
it.

 So Scott will be getting my vote in the post (as well as a cheque ;)


