like this:

Dim tags.TagItem(3)

tags(0)=#NP_Entry,?newproc
tags(1)=#NP_Name,"My New Task"
tags(2)=#TAG_DONE,0

*proc.l=CreateNewProc_(tags(0))

MouseWait

End

newproc:
Nprint "hello world"
RTS

It doesn`t work. 

Any idea?

