X-Original-Subject: 
Subject: Fonts

Hello y`all,

  Ok,. this one has been bugging me for ages now,. And I`ve always wondered
how to do it,.

How do you get the width of a Proportional font character?

IE, so that you can determine the width in pixels of a string of
characters,
to position them properly on your display? 

Any Ideas?

Cyaz l8rz..
-- 
<tsb>
<tsb>Contacting Me:
