<tsb>



@ENDNODE
@NODE "Mail_258" "Re: Fonts"
 (envelope-from D.McMinn@eee.rgu.ac.uk)
    11 Dec 98 09:41:43 0
From: "David Mcminn" <D.McMinn@eee.rgu.ac.uk>
Organization: The Robert Gordon University, E&EE
Date: Fri, 11 Dec 1998 09:41:38 -0000
encoding: Quoted-printable
Subject: Re: Fonts

Hi Loki,

 Just joined the list?

CNIF NOT_READ_THESE_BEFORE=3D1
If you have a window (#winnum) open, and your font is loaded (#fontnum) th=
en:
text$=3D"Been done at least"
WindowFont #fontnum
stringwidth.w =3D TextLength_(RastPort(#winnum), &text$, Len(text$))

...OR...
if you want the width of the font, but don't have a window (needs 
amigalibsii.res)
DEFTYPE._RastPort rp
InitRastPort_ &rp
SetFont_ &rp,Peek.l(Addr IntuiFont(#fontnum) + 8)
text$=3D"1000 times before"
stringwidth.w =3D TextLength_(&rp, &text$, Len(text$))
CEND

;)


|) /\ \/ ][ |)   |\/| =A9 |\/| ][ |\| |\|
  d.mcminn@eee.rgu.ac.uk ICQ=3D16827694
  http://members.xoom.com/David_McMinn


