opi.plastic aka emil churned out *this* drivel :


> Yello,
> 
> I try to load few shapes, and display it on window as gadgets
> and i recive a funny efect ;) all shapes looks this same :)
> But i don't understand why? I try to do manualy (in exampel im
> using data$) and it don't change anything :)
> 
> Where i go wrong?! Sorry, i don't attach "winc" include ;)
> it is simple statement for centering window on screen
> 
> ps.i lost my fdconver, could somebody send it to me?
> 
> zdroofka!

You aren't updating the x variable, so it's loading them all as
Shape x (which is zero here, since it hasn't been defined)...

A simple x+1 in the Repeat:Until loop will fix it ;)

Get newfdconvert from aminet dev/basic/ :)

See ya,
-- 
