I'm not sure, but I asked the Blitz support guy here in Australia
about 3 years ago and he said not.

I gave up using listview and use GTScroller and print the lines as
needed.  I only use one colour per line but it shouldn't be a problem
(I use different colours each line).  There may be some sneaky system
pokes, but I don't trust them!!

If you like I can extract the relevant bits and send them to you. 
take a few days tho'.

Cheers

