--=_=8<==MD236700552-2E79862B==8<=_=
Encoding: 7bit

Someone on the list (sorry I've forgotten who) asked about
multi-colour lines in a ListView.  I promised some code which uses a
GTScroller so you can (have to) print the lines yourself and so you
can do whatever colours you want.  Just use multiple PRINT commands
for each line, separating them by colourchanges.

The code is messy, but works, and is attached

It started out as a text editor or something from BUM 5 or 6.  I've
just hacked it to death.

If anyone can help by telling me how to avoid the 

Select ReportNumber
     case 1
         NextItem List1()
   etc. ad nauseam
end select

Then I'd be really pleased.

Also, if anyone who has working code to use the GTScroller buttons,
I'd love to have a look.

Thanks

-- 
Tony Rolfe
Amiga 2000, 68030/25, 1+4Mb
www.shoalhaven.net.au/edgewater

--=_=8<==MD236700552-2E79862B==8<=_=
Encoding: plain (7/8 bit)
Content-Disposition: attachment; filename="Scroller.asc"
X-MD2-FilePath: Blitz2:Examples/Scroller.asc

;  This is the basic GTScroller routine used for
;  all my reports and "pick-one-of-the-following"
;  routines.  I've hacked a lot of special case code
;  from it but it is still pretty messy.

;  THIS WILL NOT COMPILE AS IS!!

;  Before calling this routine the caller must set up a
;  number of variables to define the report's
;  characteristics.  There are also a number of numeric
;  constants defined earlier in the code which are not
;  included here.

;  As you will see, it handles umpteen different reports etc.
;  I've included enough to give a flavour without listing every
;  gosub'ed routine for every report.

;  Please feel free to email me privately or through the list
;  if you want anything explained.  I've never been any good at
;  documenting my personal code.

;  Regards
;        TonyR


.process_scroller

Saved_GadList = GadList  ; Save background gadget list number
GadList = #MM02          ; This is Number 2
Selected = 0             ; Nothing selected yet.

x = 0                    ; Window positions
y = 0                    ; ... some deleted code can change these
w = 640
h = DispHeight
BoxLeft  = 4
BoxRight = 608

If ReportHeading$ = ""
   TopMargin    = 0.25   ; Gap from top of window
   BottomMargin = 2.875  ; ... and from bottom
Else
   TopMargin    = 1.675
   BottomMargin = 2.5
EndIf

If ReportFlags >= #MultiSelect  ; Needs buttons on the bottom
   BottomMargin + 1             ; ... so make room for them
EndIf

BoxTop       = TopMargin*8
BoxBottom    = DispHeight-(BottomMargin*8)+1
BoxHeight    = BoxBottom-BoxTop
VisibleLines = Int(BoxHeight/8)    ;visible display lines.
Borders On
BorderPens 2,1

; I've never managed to use the arrows built into the GTScroller
; properly, so I use Text gadgets.

l = BoxLeft+BoxRight
TextGadget #MM02,l+4,BoxBottom-22,0,#MM02_Up,"^"
TextGadget #MM02,l+4,BoxBottom-10,0,#MM02_Down,"v"
GTScroller #MM02,#MM02_Scroller,l,BoxTop-13,16,BoxHeight-20,"",#GT_Vertical+#GT_Immediate,VisibleLines,Count,Top

;  Add buttons to bottom of window if required

If ReportHeading$ <> ""
   Button_Y - 11        ; Adjust for Window Border
   Gosub buttons
   Button_Y + 11        ; Adjust back again
Else
   Button_Y - 12        ; Adjust for Window Border and heading
   Gosub buttons
   Button_Y + 12        ; Adjust back again
EndIf

ScreensBitMap 0,0

DefaultIDCMP $200+$100+$40+$20+$10 ; Default IDCMP Flags

If ReportFlags AND #Selectable     ; But, for selectable reports
   AddIDCMP $8                     ; ... check mouse button events
EndIf

If ReportFlags AND #KeyPress  ; And, for Key selectable reports
   AddIDCMP $400              ; ... check key press events
EndIf

Window 1,x,y,w,h,$1408,ReportTitle$,1,2,#MM02

AttachGTList #MM02,1
If Count > 0            ; No of entries in list
   GadgetBorder BoxLeft,BoxTop,BoxRight,BoxHeight
EndIf

If ReportHeading$ <> ""
   BorderPens   2,1
   GadgetBorder 4,2,BoxRight,7
   WLocate 4,2
   Print  ReportHeading$
EndIf

If ReportFlags & #Message
   Message{ReportMessage$}
EndIf

BitMapOutput 0
Colour #fc,#bc

SetMenu Menu_No
oTop = -1
The_One = -1
If Count > 0
   Gosub refresh_scroller
   Entry_to_Print = 1
   Gosub position_array
EndIf
Last = -1
Cancelled = False
Key$ = ""

Repeat
   ev = WaitEvent
   If EventWindow = 1       ; Only process events for the scroller window
      Select ev
         Case $8            ; Mouse button hit
            If MButtons = 1
               CurrentTime_ &eSecs.l,&eMicros.l
               mx = EMouseX
               my = EMouseY - WTopOff
               If mx > BoxLeft + 2 AND mx < BoxLeft + BoxRight + 2 AND my > BoxTop AND my < BoxTop + (VisibleLines * 8)
                  LineNo = Int((my-BoxTop)/8)-1
                  Entry_to_Print = LineNo + Top + 1
                  Gosub position_array
                  CurrentTime_ &eSecs.l,&eMicros.l
                  This = LineNo + Top + 1
                  If This < Count
                     If This <> Last
                        If (ReportFlags & #Multi) = 0
                           If Last <> -1
                              Line_to_Print = Last - Top
                              Entry_to_Print = Last
                              Gosub position_array
                              Gosub set_default_bc
                              If ReportNumber <> #Loans
                                 Gosub print_a_line
                              EndIf
                           EndIf
                        EndIf
                        Line_to_Print = This - Top
                        Entry_to_Print = This
                        Gosub flip_scroller_line
                        Last = This
                     Else
                        Line_to_Print = This - Top
                        Entry_to_Print = This
                        If DoubleClick_(sSecs.l,sMicros.l,eSecs,eMicros)
                           The_One = This
                           Top = The_One
                           Gosub set_default_bc
                           ev = $200
                           If ReportFlags & #Multi
                              Gosub flip_scroller_line
                              Selected - 1
                              If Selected > Max_Selectable
                                 ret = RTEZRequest("Error","Too Many Items Selected","OK")
                                 ev = 8
                              EndIf
                           EndIf
                        Else
                           Gosub flip_scroller_line
                        EndIf
                     EndIf
                     sSecs = eSecs
                     sMicros = eMicros
                  EndIf
               EndIf
            EndIf
         Case $20              ; Gadget down
            Select GadgetHit
               Case #MM02_Scroller
                  Repeat
                     Top = EventCode
                     Gosub refresh_scroller
                  Until WaitEvent=64
               Case #MM02_Up
                  Entry_to_Print = Top - 1
                  Gosub position_array
                  Line_to_Print = 0
                  While Event <> 64 AND Top > 0
                     VWait
                     Scroll x+BoxLeft+2,y+BoxTop+WTopOff,BoxRight+2,BoxHeight-8,x+BoxLeft+2,y+BoxTop+WTopOff+8
                     Gosub print_a_line
                     Select ReportNumber
                        Case #Primary
                           PrevItem ReportLines()
                        Case #Loans
                           PrevItem ReportLines()
                        Case #AssetRegister
                           PrevItem Assets()
                        Case #ChequeBook
                           PrevItem ChequeBook()
                        Case #CustomerList
                           PrevItem Customers()
                        Case #DepositList
                           PrevItem Deposits()
                        Case #SupplierList
                           PrevItem Suppliers()
                        Case #Expenses
                           PrevItem Expenses()
                        Case #Advertisers
                           PrevItem Advertisers()
                        Case #PettyCash
                           PrevItem PettyCash()
                        Case #Deferred
                           PrevItem Deferred()
                        Case #Agents
                           PrevItem Agents()
                        Case #BMCin
                           PrevItem BMCin()
                        Case #BMCout
                           PrevItem BMCout()
                        Case #Cards
                           PrevItem Cards()
                        Case #Accounts
                           PrevItem Accounts()
                     End Select
                     Top - 1
                     GTSetAttrs #MM02,#MM02_Scroller,#GTSC_Top,Top
                  Wend
                  oTop=Top
               Case #MM02_Down
                  Entry_to_Print = Top + VisibleLines
                  Gosub position_array
                  Line_to_Print = VisibleLines-1
                  While Event <> 64 AND Top < Count-VisibleLines
                     VWait
                     Scroll x+BoxLeft+2,y+BoxTop+WTopOff+8,BoxRight+2,BoxHeight-8,x+BoxLeft+2,y+BoxTop+WTopOff
                     Gosub print_a_line
                     Select ReportNumber
                        Case #Primary
                           NextItem ReportLines()
                        Case #Loans
                           NextItem ReportLines()
                        Case #AssetRegister
                           NextItem Assets()
                        Case #ChequeBook
                           NextItem ChequeBook()
                        Case #CustomerList
                           NextItem Customers()
                        Case #DepositList
                           NextItem Deposits()
                        Case #SupplierList
                           NextItem Suppliers()
                        Case #Expenses
                           NextItem Expenses()
                        Case #Advertisers
                           NextItem Advertisers()
                        Case #PettyCash
                           NextItem PettyCash()
                        Case #Deferred
                           NextItem Deferred()
                        Case #Agents
                           NextItem Agents()
                        Case #BMCin
                           NextItem BMCin()
                        Case #BMCout
                           NextItem BMCout()
                        Case #Cards
                           NextItem Cards()
                        Case #Accounts
                           NextItem Accounts()
                     End Select
                     Top + 1
                     GTSetAttrs #MM02,#MM02_Scroller,#GTSC_Top,Top
                  Wend
                  oTop=Top
            End Select
         Case $40              ; Gadget Up
            Select GadgetHit
               Case #MM02_Scroller
                  Top = EventCode
                  Gosub refresh_scroller
                  oTop=Top
               Case #MM02_Sideways
                  LeftCol = EventCode
                  Gosub scroll_sideways
               Case #AllButton
                  Selected = Count
                  Select ReportNumber
                     Case #Primary
                        ResetList ReportLines()
                        While NextItem(ReportLines())
                           ReportLines()\Selected = #sc
                        Wend
                     Case #Accounts
                        ResetList Accounts()
                        While NextItem(Accounts())
                           Accounts()\bc = #sc
                        Wend
                  End Select
                  oTop = -1
                  Gosub refresh_scroller
                  oTop = Top
               Case #NoneButton
                  Selected = 0
                  Select ReportNumber
                     Case #Primary
                        ResetList ReportLines()
                        While NextItem(ReportLines())
                           ReportLines()\Selected = #bc
                        Wend
                     Case #Accounts
                        ResetList Accounts()
                        While NextItem(Accounts())
                           Accounts()\bc = #bc
                        Wend
                  End Select
                  oTop = -1
                  Gosub refresh_scroller
                  oTop = Top
               Case #UseButton
                  If Selected > Max_Selectable
                     ret = RTEZRequest("Error","Too Many Items Selected","OK")
                     ev = 8
                  EndIf
               Case #CancelButton
                  Cancelled = True
                  ev = $200
            End Select
         Case $100                ; MenuPick
            Select MenuHit
               Case 0
                  Select ItemHit
                     Case 0: Gosub print_report
                     Case 1:
                        Cancelled = True
                        ev = $200
                  End Select
               Case 1
                  Select ItemHit
                     Case 0
                        WindowOutput 1
                        If reconcile_mode
                           reconcile_mode = False
                           Message{"Edit Mode now set"}
                           MenuItem  2,0,1,0,"Reconcile Mode"
                        Else
                           reconcile_mode = True
                           Message{"Reconcile mode set - Cleared balance is "+Dollars{Cleared_Total,0}}
                           MenuItem  2,0,1,0,"Edit Mode"
                        EndIf
                        BitMapOutput 0
                  End Select
            End Select
         Case $200               ; Close button hit
            Cancelled = True
         Case $400               ; Key Press Detected
            Gosub build_key
            VWait #KeyDelay      ; Wait for a few seconds
            While Event = $400   ; Was another key pressed?
               Gosub build_key   ; Yes - go append it to the key
               VWait #KeyDelay   ; Then try again
            Wend
            Select ReportNumber
               Case #CustomerList
                  Top = -1
                  FirstItem Customers()
                  While Key$ >= UCase$(Customers()\Name) AND Top <= Count
                     NextItem Customers()
                     Top + 1
                  Wend
               Case #SupplierList
                  Top = -1
                  FirstItem Suppliers()
                  While Key$ >= UCase$(Suppliers()\Name) AND Top <= Count
                     NextItem Suppliers()
                     Top + 1
                  Wend
            End Select
            Gosub refresh_scroller
            GTSetAttrs #MM02,#MM02_Scroller,#GTSC_Top,Top
      End Select
   Else
      ev = 0
   EndIf
Until ev=$200 OR (ev = 64 AND GadgetHit > #AllButton)

reconcile_mode = False
MenuItem  2,0,1,0,"Reconcile Mode"
Free Window 1
Free GTList #MM02
Free GadgetList #MM02
FlushEvents
*win.window = Addr Window(0)
If *win\_window
   Use Window 0
   Activate 0
EndIf

GadList = Saved_GadList
Return

.refresh_scroller

If Top > Count-VisibleLines
   Top = Count-VisibleLines
EndIf

If Top < 0
   Top = 0
EndIf

If Top<>oTop
   oTop=Top
   Boxf x+BoxLeft+2,y+BoxTop+WTopOff,x+BoxRight+6,y+BoxBottom+WTopOff,#bc
   Entry_to_Print = Top
   Gosub position_array
   Max_Lines = Count - Top
   If Count - Top > VisibleLines
      Max_Lines = VisibleLines
   EndIf
   For Line_to_Print = 0 To Max_Lines - 1
      Gosub print_a_line
      Select ReportNumber
         Case #Primary
            NextItem ReportLines()
         Case #Loans
            NextItem ReportLines()
         Case #AssetRegister
            NextItem Assets()
         Case #ChequeBook
            NextItem ChequeBook()
         Case #CustomerList
            NextItem Customers()
         Case #DepositList
            NextItem Deposits()
         Case #SupplierList
            NextItem Suppliers()
         Case #Expenses
            NextItem Expenses()
         Case #Advertisers
            NextItem Advertisers()
         Case #PettyCash
            NextItem PettyCash()
         Case #Deferred
            NextItem Deferred()
         Case #Agents
            NextItem Agents()
         Case #BMCin
            NextItem BMCin()
         Case #BMCout
            NextItem BMCout()
         Case #Cards
            NextItem Cards()
         Case #Accounts
            NextItem Accounts()
      End Select
   Next
EndIf

Return

.print_a_line

If Line_to_Print < VisibleLines AND Line_to_Print >= 0
   BitMapOutput 0
   Locate ((x+BoxLeft)/8)+1,(y/8)+1.375+TopMargin+Line_to_Print

   Select ReportNumber
      Case #Primary
         Colour #fc,ReportLines()\Selected
         NPrint LSet$(ReportLines()\ListString,#LineWidth)
      Case #Loans
         Colour #fc,ReportLines()\Selected
         NPrint LSet$(ReportLines()\ListString,#LineWidth)
      Case #AssetRegister
         Colour #fc,Assets()\bc
         Gosub print_asset_line
      Case #ChequeBook
         If ChequeBook()\Cleared
            Colour #cc,ChequeBook()\bc
         Else
            Colour #fc,ChequeBook()\bc
         EndIf
         Gosub print_cbk_line
      Case #CustomerList
         Colour #fc,Customers()\bc
         Gosub print_customer_line
      Case #DepositList
         Colour #fc,Deposits()\bc
         Gosub print_deposit_line
      Case #SupplierList
         Colour #fc,Suppliers()\bc
         Gosub print_supplier_line
      Case #Expenses
         Colour #fc,Expenses()\bc
         Gosub print_expenses_line
      Case #Advertisers
         Colour #fc,Advertisers()\bc
         Gosub print_advertisers_line
      Case #PettyCash
         Colour #fc,PettyCash()\bc
         Gosub print_petty_cash_line
      Case #Deferred
         Colour #fc,Deferred()\bc
         Gosub print_deferred_line
      Case #Agents
         Colour #fc,Agents()\bc
         Gosub print_agents_line
      Case #BMCin
         Colour #fc,BMCin()\bc
         Gosub print_BMCin_line
      Case #BMCout
         Colour #fc,BMCout()\bc
         Gosub print_BMCout_line
      Case #Cards
         Colour #fc,Cards()\bc
         Gosub print_Cards_line
      Case #Accounts
         Colour #fc,Accounts()\bc
         Gosub print_Accounts_line
   End Select
EndIf

Return

.position_array

Blank_Line = False

Select ReportNumber
   Case #Primary
      FirstItem ReportLines()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem ReportLines()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
      If StripTrail$(ReportLines()\ListString,32) = ""
         Blank_Line = True
      EndIf
   Case #Loans
      FirstItem ReportLines()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem ReportLines()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
      If StripTrail$(ReportLines()\ListString,32) = ""
         Blank_Line = True
      EndIf
   Case #AssetRegister
      FirstItem Assets()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem Assets()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
   Case #ChequeBook
      FirstItem ChequeBook()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem ChequeBook()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
   Case #CustomerList
      FirstItem Customers()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem Customers()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
   Case #DepositList
      Gosub position_deposits
   Case #SupplierList
      FirstItem Suppliers()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem Suppliers()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
   Case #Expenses
      FirstItem Expenses()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem Expenses()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
   Case #Advertisers
      FirstItem Advertisers()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem Advertisers()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
   Case #PettyCash
      FirstItem PettyCash()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem PettyCash()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
      If PettyCash()\Kind <> 2
         Blank_Line = True
      EndIf
   Case #Deferred
      FirstItem Deferred()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem Deferred()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
   Case #Agents
      FirstItem Agents()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem Agents()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
   Case #BMCin
      FirstItem BMCin()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem BMCin()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
   Case #BMCout
      FirstItem BMCout()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem BMCout()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
   Case #Cards
      FirstItem Cards()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem Cards()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
   Case #Accounts
      FirstItem Accounts()
      While Entry_to_Print > 0
         NextItem Accounts()
         Entry_to_Print - 1
      Wend
End Select

Return

.flip_scroller_line

If Line_to_Print >= 0
   Gosub position_array
   Select ReportNumber
      Case #Primary
         ReportLines()\Selected = 2 - ReportLines()\Selected
         Selected - 1 + ReportLines()\Selected
      Case #Loans
         PushItem ReportLines()
         a$ = Left$(ReportLines()\ListString,1)
         While a$ = " " AND StripTrail$(ReportLines()\ListString,32) <> ""
            If PrevItem(ReportLines())
               Line_to_Print - 1
               a$ = Left$(ReportLines()\ListString,1)
            Else
               a$ = "."
            EndIf
         Wend
         If StripTrail$(ReportLines()\ListString,32) <> ""
            ReportLines()\Selected = 2 - ReportLines()\Selected
            Gosub print_a_line
         EndIf
         If NextItem(ReportLines())
            Line_to_Print + 1
            a$ = Left$(ReportLines()\ListString,1)
            While a$ = " "
               If StripTrail$(ReportLines()\ListString,32) <> ""
                  ReportLines()\Selected = 2 - ReportLines()\Selected
                  Gosub print_a_line
               EndIf
               If NextItem(ReportLines())
                  Line_to_Print + 1
                  a$ = Left$(ReportLines()\ListString,1)
               Else
                  a$ = "."
               EndIf
            Wend
         EndIf
         PopItem ReportLines()
      Case #AssetRegister
         Assets()\bc = 2 - Assets()\bc
         Selected - 1 + Assets()\bc
      Case #ChequeBook
         ChequeBook()\bc = 2 - ChequeBook()\bc
      Case #CustomerList
         Customers()\bc = 2 - Customers()\bc
      Case #DepositList
         Deposits()\bc = 2 - Deposits()\bc
      Case #SupplierList
         Suppliers()\bc = 2 - Suppliers()\bc
      Case #Expenses
         Expenses()\bc = 2 - Expenses()\bc
      Case #Advertisers
         Advertisers()\bc = 2 - Advertisers()\bc
      Case #PettyCash
         PettyCash()\bc = 2 - PettyCash()\bc
      Case #Deferred
         Deferred()\bc = 2 - Deferred()\bc
      Case #Agents
         Agents()\bc = 2 - Agents()\bc
      Case #BMCin
         BMCin()\bc = 2 - BMCin()\bc
      Case #BMCout
         BMCout()\bc = 2 - BMCout()\bc
      Case #Cards
         Cards()\bc = 2 - Cards()\bc
      Case #Accounts
         Accounts()\bc = 2 - Accounts()\bc
         Selected - 1 + Accounts()\bc
   End Select
   If ReportNumber <> #Loans
      Gosub print_a_line
   EndIf
EndIf

Return

.set_default_bc

Select ReportNumber
   Case #Primary
      ReportLines()\Selected = False
   Case #Loans
      PushItem ReportLines()
      a$ = Left$(ReportLines()\ListString,1)
      While a$ = " " AND StripTrail$(ReportLines()\ListString,32) <> ""
         If PrevItem(ReportLines())
            Line_to_Print - 1
            a$ = Left$(ReportLines()\ListString,1)
         Else
            a$ = "."
         EndIf
      Wend
      If StripTrail$(ReportLines()\ListString,32) <> ""
         ReportLines()\Selected = False
         Gosub print_a_line
      EndIf
      If NextItem(ReportLines())
         Line_to_Print + 1
         a$ = Left$(ReportLines()\ListString,1)
         While a$ = " "
            If StripTrail$(ReportLines()\ListString,32) <> ""
               ReportLines()\Selected = False
               Gosub print_a_line
            EndIf
            If NextItem(ReportLines())
               Line_to_Print + 1
               a$ = Left$(ReportLines()\ListString,1)
            Else
               a$ = "."
            EndIf
         Wend
      EndIf
      PopItem ReportLines()
   Case #AssetRegister
      Assets()\bc = #bc
   Case #ChequeBook
      ChequeBook()\bc = #bc
   Case #CustomerList
      Customers()\bc = #bc
   Case #DepositList
      Deposits()\bc = #bc
   Case #SupplierList
      Suppliers()\bc = #bc
   Case #Expenses
      Expenses()\bc = #bc
   Case #Advertisers
      Advertisers()\bc = #bc
   Case #PettyCash
      PettyCash()\bc = #bc
   Case #Deferred
      Deferred()\bc = #bc
   Case #Agents
      Agents()\bc = #bc
   Case #BMCin
      BMCin()\bc = #bc
   Case #BMCout
      BMCout()\bc = #bc
   Case #Cards
      Cards()\bc = #bc
   Case #Accounts
      Accounts()\bc = #bc
End Select

Return

.scroll_sideways

WindowOutput 1
If ReportNumber = #Expenses
   Gosub print_expenses_headings
EndIf
VWait
Boxf   FixedPixels+BoxLeft,BoxTop+WTopOff,BoxRight+8,BoxBottom+WTopOff-1,#bc
Use BitMap 1
GetaShape 0,LeftCol*ColWidth*8,Top*8,ColWidth*16,VisibleLines*8
Use BitMap 0
Blit 0,(FixedWidth+1)*8,BoxTop+WTopOff,Off
GTSetAttrs #MM02,#MM02_Sideways,#GTSC_Top,LeftCol

Return



