t
> it says it's included in Acidlibs :((

 What says its included in acidlibs? Theres no way that you can get a libr=
ary 
inserted into acidlibs, as theres no program to remake that file. You shou=
ld 
use lib nums of around 200 and above for the system libraries (ones you co=
nvert 
with FDConvert). Thats what Acid tried to do before they disappeared, so i=
ts 
probably easier to keep doing that.

 Have you run makedeflibs after doing fdconvert?

> I've tried different libnums and renaming the mpega.library1 but to no
> avail..

> attached is the FD for mpega.library, hope someone can help here :)

 No it wasn't attached.


