@NODE "Mail_534" "Re: RastPort"
 id 0zqE8N-0001l7-00; Wed, 16 Dec 1998 10:24:54 +0000
 (envelope-from D.McMinn@eee.rgu.ac.uk)
    16 Dec 98 10:23:46 0
From: "David Mcminn" <D.McMinn@eee.rgu.ac.uk>
Organization: The Robert Gordon University, E&EE
Date: Wed, 16 Dec 1998 10:23:38 -0000
encoding: Quoted-printable
Subject: Re: RastPort

Hi Steven,
 Ignore everything I've said, its all a lie. I didn't realise there was a 
Bitmap library in the NLibs, so I now realise you've done everything in th=
e 
NLibs. OK, well here's what to do:

bmpid.l =3D NBitmap(0,320,200,1)
NDrawingOutPut NBitMapRastPort



|) /\ \/ ][ |)   |\/| =A9 |\/| ][ |\| |\|
