Subject: Resettimer & Ticks Replacement

Hallooo!

Oki here is the thing, I'm writing a proggie that executes another prog
using the

#execute_# Command, it also times how long it takes for the other program to
run.. eg.

#resettimer
#execute_ ("PROG TO TEST",0,0
#seconds,l=ticks/50
#nprint seconds

okay what I'd like to know is.. what would be the asm/system equivalent of
the Resettimer/ticks commands as these add a Huge amount of code, making
the exe over 5k bigger?

Cya
