> Use the #SystemDate# and #Seconds# commands inside a loop to count the
> number of #Ticks# that have passed since the last second passed!
> 
> <pseudo-example, probably won't work just as is>
> 
> b.b=0
> a.b=#Seconds#
> #While# a=#Seconds#
>   ;   #VWait#   ;   Might wanna use that if you're in AMIGA mode
> #Wend#   ;   That was to make sure you've waited for a complete second
> a=#Seconds#   ;   to pass, first...
