@NODE "Mail_600" "Re: Screen Stuff"
 id 0zubBy-0006zR-00; Mon, 28 Dec 1998 11:50:35 +0000
From: "Simon Hitchen" <simon@gadge.u-net.com>
Organization: Gadge Software
Date: 28 Dec 98 10:28:54 +0000
Subject: Re: Screen Stuff
X-Face: )#:\SgS;n&m:TktiESD\s{QJR~&.8$WC/pC<~`=Sc>W'))hz/k{7<^'z_(G>|D=$r.a;H.&@5ZL88X;ufE`I:kH'VW
Encoding: 7bit

> Hello.
> 
> Does anyone know how to get the height of the titlebar, and/or the width of
> the Gadget ?

This'll get the BarHeight, dunno about gadget widths though....

-----------------------------------------
; don't forget to make amigalibs.res resident :-)
FindScreen 0
*scr.Screen=Peek.l (Addr Screen(0))
tbar.w=*scr\BarHeight+1
NPrint tbar
Repeat
  WaitTOF_
Until Joyb(0)
End
-----------------------------------------


-- 

Bye f'now

Simon

simon@gadge.u-net.com
http://www.gadge.u-net.com
ICQ: 22707489

