From: Curt Esser <camge@ix.netcom.com>
Date: Mon, 28 Dec 1998 06:03:48 -0500
Subject: Re: Screen Stuff
Encoding: quoted-printable

Hi Mikkel

On 27-Dec-98, Mikkel L=F8kke wrote:
> Hello.
> =

> Does anyone know how to get the height of the titlebar, and/or the widt=
h
of
> the Gadget ?

You'll need Amigalibs.res...

*SC.Screen=3DPeek.l(Addr Screen(0))     ; get a pointer to your screen
ht.b=3D*SC.Screen\BarHeight             ; read the titlebar height

Don't know about the gadget, though...  =


Later...
