read my mail recently. Anyway, the method I use in Radioaction is to use the
FNS print commands that come with the Blitz Support Suite. They work like a
dream on bitmaps. You can use any size of text, too. If you want to replace
the background behind the text after use, grab the shape of the area behind
the text.

